ttp://pub14.ezboard.com/uhaass.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Haass</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 332<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/3/02 8:41:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3407.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Just a brief summary... </span><hr size=1> Quite honestly, your armor looks good.  The thing that is standing out to me right now is your primary hand.  I used a GSC for a couple levels in my low 50's too and it really just doesn't hold taunt very well.  Frosty offhand is great, but i'd look towards trying to get a tad faster primary wep...even a jade mace outperforms a GSC.  I do understand the price difference, but I was a lot happier when I ditched that goranga club.<br><br>Try to grab one of the many 10/18 weapons if ya can, price is dropping fast on those.  CBoL, crafted velium, Seb dirk, etc.  That will hold ya over on weapons till 60 and you can go back to making the small upgrades on your armor. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=3407.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=3407.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3407.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=3407.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a F